  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.header": "直观的理解电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_1": "想象一个首尾相连的线路。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_10": "在这种情况下，这种运动会使灯泡的灯丝升温，并使灯丝热得发光。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_11": "请注意输入的点的数量等于输出的点的数量。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_12": "这就是基尔霍夫电流定律。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_2": "在这条线上放置一些点，把它们看作是电。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_3": "这就像一条链条。这些点可以移动，但它们无法彼此分离。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_4": "电压源试图推动这一链条。它们试图从一侧推动，并向另一侧施加拉力。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_5": "请注意，这些点的数量始终保持不变。这些点本身并不代表能量，它们的移动才是电能的表现形式。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_6": "这实际上是一个短路。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_7": "这里没有电阻，电压源能够快速移动这些点！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_8": "将一个设备接入到电路里。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_9": "这些设备利用这些点的运动来获得能量。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.header": "连接线缆",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_1": "接线端子和线缆可用于传输电能。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_2": "要移除已连接的线缆，可使用空线轴。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_3": "绝缘电缆可以染色。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.header": "在未加载的区块传输电力",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.text_1": "在已加载的区块范围之外，电力仍能正常传输。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.header": "控制电流的方向",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_1": "这是一个好东西",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_2": "如果二极管的正极与电源正极相连，它将允许电流通过....",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_3": "....负极与电源负极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_4": "这被称为单向导电性",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_5": "否则，电流将无法通过二极管",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_6": "反接的二极管将无法导电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.header": "列车电气化",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_1": "接触网支架会自动连接到附近的柱状物",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_2": "接触网可以为列车供电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_3": "要使用电力的列车需要有一个受电弓来与接触网接触...",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_4": "以及一个电动机...",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_5": "要给接触网供电，需要将接触网与电源正极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_6": "将电源负极与接地针相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_7": "2500 V",
